feat(api): implement B2B REST API with ML-DSA-87 JWT auth (#57, #60)

Edge proxy server (Hono) translating REST calls to SmartCircuit
invocations on the eStream network. Implements all 14 endpoints from
the OpenAPI spec with scope-based authorization, visibility tier field
filtering, cursor-based pagination, rate limiting, and audit logging.

Auth: ML-DSA-87 JWT verification, OAuth2 client credentials flow,
13 scopes, 4 visibility tiers (public/buyer/auditor/owner).

Endpoints: credits (3), attestations (2), retirements (2),
marketplace (2), contracts (2), audit (2), governance (1).

Closes #57, closes #60
